# Diagho Toolkit

## What is Diagho Toolkit ?

Diagho Toolkit is a python library which will read and parse a genomic file and return a generator with a pydantic model.

## What database is used ?

- OMIM
- HGNC
- HPO
- gnomAD
- gnomAD constraint
- VCF
- Fasta
- GFF3

## What pydantic model is returned ?

- Clinvar
- Feature
- Gene
- GnomAD
- GnomAD_constraint
- Pathology
- Region
- Sequence
- Symptom
- Variant
